{"tid":2192710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時唔係唔想喺茶記食，而係真係唔值得咁貴食個頹飯加態度差","createTime":"2020-09-07T09:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:49:44.000Z","uid":192748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7740f230d1df98192ccb7c41630ba8b5e5144fd5","tid":2192710,"uid":192748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:45:53.000Z","msg":"茶記係香港一個好有特色嘅飲食文化嚟，但係好多依家收緊5,60蚊一個餐,冇營養之餘大部份茶記伙記態度都好惡劣，環境衛生都好差。 有時都想幫襯下本土特色，但係有時路過睇住食客枱上面嗰pat頹汁 收你5,60蚊，真係比唔落錢去食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然話係香港本土飲食特色文化，但係呢種模式嘅飲食真係仲有好大嘅改善空間。"},{"pid":"3e916150075b4fb3af4924cc1ed702c7ce93568f","tid":2192710,"uid":208323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"港島態度差過九龍<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1501d572691e739d2003014cdd4930b009b19d3d","tid":2192710,"uid":313426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"咁仲有啲乜嘢食<br />\n大家樂？"},{"pid":"4bb690819ae152d540f28d1c74630a6ee7620d20","tid":2192710,"uid":366166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"燒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfe97d9e27be34281e8719ecb3a18776e29d93f","tid":2192710,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"最大問題係<br />\n通常啲餐都係澱粉太高，蛋白質太低，完全唔係健康飲食"}]}